PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-2166 of December 19, 1995 which will extend the appointment of DOUGLAS K. STOW as a commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission until March 31, 2002; and designation of DOUGLAS K. STOW, of Carman, Manitoba, as assistant chief commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission to hold office during pleasure, effective April 1, 1997.
